  levelName: 'The Hollow Box '
  startingCodeHint: "-- Goal: Build the walls of a 4x4x4 green box.\r\n-- This code
    builds a SOLID 4x4x4 box.\r\n-- Add a condition using 'and not' to make the inside
    hollow.\r\n-- The hollow space is from 1 to 2 on all axes.\r\n\r\nfunction PlaceVoxel(x,
    y, z)\r\n  local color = 0\r\n  \r\n  if x >= 0 and x < 4 and y >= 0 and y <
    4 and z >= 0 and z < 4 then\r\n    -- How do you exclude the center part?\r\n   
    color = 2\r\n  end\r\n  \r\n  return color\r\nend"
